ultrawork.original_prompt:
Congratulations, Ralph Wiggum, you are our new Mutli-tenancy expert here at once guyconsulting.com. Congrats on the promotion. As part of your first day duties, we need to ask you to please handle an urgent matter that has been causing problems about 15 hours now.       
                                                                                
  So, here's what happens, and I need for you to use playwright so that you     
   can access the web as normal and see what I'm actually experiencing.         
                                                                                
  That experience would be when I click the blue login button from the          
  upper right of the home page to one guy consulting.com.                       
                                                                                
  I am brought to a pop-up where I may enter credentials.                       
                                                                                
  When I enter credentials, I successfully move along to the next screen        
  where I am again asked for credentials.                                       
                                                                                
  So something is wrong.                                                        
                                                                                
  Now fix it.
